{"tid":1687797,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"300市民和你跑唱《榮光》","createTime":"2019-11-02T05:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T06:01:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"381604ac899f3d450c2d50972773ab86394f59c4","tid":1687797,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:44:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191102/2USH7YOPU2DQHNMDBSH6PNTDCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191102%2F2USH7YOPU2DQHNMDBSH6PNTDCY%2F&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8OzsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=8d67870d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191102%2F2USH7YOPU2DQHNMDBSH6PNTDCY%2F&h=c86da34f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191102/2USH7YOPU2DQHNMDBSH6PNTDCY/</a><br />\n<br />\n300市民和你跑唱《榮光》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方早前濫用《公安條例》要求跑會為超過30人的練跑活動申請不反對通知書，引起全城譁然，昨晚逾300名市民在西環中山紀念公園舉行「和你跑」活動，一齊練跑操體能，一直跑往灣仔金紫荊廣場，沿途亮起手機燈並高叫「香港人反抗」等口號，照亮海傍一帶，其間並無警員到場。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警：維園聚會 逾50人參與即違法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/KOooR9tn4olvlvk-fOH3DKycEZQ=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/JQLJD3MMEG5QDWAIUITS4AWPCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FKOooR9tn4olvlvk-fOH3DKycEZQ%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FJQLJD3MMEG5QDWAIUITS4AWPCY.jpg&h=b29495c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逾300名跑手由中山紀念公園跑往金紫荊廣場，沿途高舉手機燈照亮海傍。王子俊攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戴口罩達到「加操」效果<br />\n<br />\n昨晚的「和你跑」活動於晚上9時開始，各跑手首先在中山紀念公園集合，大部份參加者均穿上跑衫跑褲，部份人更戴上口罩聲言要令自己呼吸更難，達到「加操」效果。各人先在公園跑熱身圈，有人頭戴電筒，亦有人亮起手機燈照明，其間大家合唱《願榮光歸香港》，又大叫「五大訴求，缺一不可」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n至晚上9時10分左右，「和你跑」開始，眾人沿海傍出發直跑往金紫荊廣場，全程約4公里。跑步期間，各跑手「練氣」高呼「香港人反抗」等口號。有男跑手更以寫上「光復香港，時代革命」的橫額作斗篷，笑言沿路有點凍要保暖。跑手陸續到達終點，眾人再高唱《願榮光歸香港》並叫口號，之後和平散去。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姜偉康<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/2bUMk_jHsGNK8c01fmyZdtdKk7U=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/UXFVPVSQS6PFLTSBUULTG2HMK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F2bUMk_jHsGNK8c01fmyZdtdKk7U%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FUXFVPVSQS6PFLTSBUULTG2HMK4.jpg&h=c9dd2a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跑手抵達金紫荊廣場後高喊口號，唱出《願榮光歸香港》後和平散去。<br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"9830bd7b8ab9448c37a9d127f341fea96813b41e","tid":1687797,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:45:49.000Z","msg":"可以唔同區搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n訓練大家跑步<br />\n一齊玩渣馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3defc20b8dd44764ac7951e53f1aebce7693d43","tid":1687797,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:47:13.000Z","msg":"有無手足係邊戴罩邊跑邊唱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d73b4086f9be01c2e6d8e764638d697694a536","tid":1687797,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://streamable.com/mm2gk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fmm2gk&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8OzsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=6afe9ea9\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/mm2gk</a><br />\n航拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d580374ff4dc53785cb8e92b75729c4fcc763475","tid":1687797,"uid":335391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63d73b4086f9be01c2e6d8e764638d697694a536","tid":1687797,"uid":261873,"like":